"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?34/49/35604?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Clindamycin (systemic): Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?8/1/8215?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Clindamycin (systemic): Pediatric drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
